snippet: Florida catcher Mike Zunino was chosen the winner of the Dick Howser Trophy as college baseball’s player of the year. Zunino is the first Florida player to win the award in its 26-year history.
lead_paragraph: Florida catcher Mike Zunino was chosen the winner of the Dick Howser Trophy as college baseball’s player of the year. Zunino is the first Florida player to win the award in its 26-year history.
